---
title: Easy Hasselback Chicken & Spiced Potatoes with Chargrilled Capsicum Relish & Apple Salad
description: Get ready to meet the chicken of your dreams! With a crispy, cheesy crust and tasty pockets of capsicum relish,
every bite is a flavour bomb. Teamed with mildly spiced roasted potatoes, this is definitely a dinner worth
staying in for.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
